creator: Aperta, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Don’t let someone else get to your dream apartment first. With the block.a app’s on-demand touring and applications, you’re no longer at the mercy of brokers and agents. Go from inquiry to application to lease in hours. You call the shots.
We provide a unique apartment touring experience for renters to tour apartments using block.a.
If the apartment is vacant, you can tour apartments on your schedule using the app to securely access. If the apartment is occupied, you can schedule a time through the app, with the current tenant giving you the inside scoop.
descriptionShort: block.a allows you to tour New York apartments in-person, on your own schedule
title: block.a -  Rental App
